snippet: ICCAuctions is offering about 1,000 corkscrews in an online sale; dozens of corkscrews on the lower end of the scale come in the shapes of peasants, bartenders, clowns, parrots, bulldogs and cats.
abstract: Eve M Kahn Antiques column; ICCAuctions is offering about 1,000 corkscrews in an online sale; dozens of corkscrews on the lower end of the scale come in the shapes of peasants, bartenders, clowns, parrots, bulldogs and cats; exhibit of Carlo Mollino furniture designs from around 1950 opens at Salon 94 on the Upper East Side.
